17
00:01:59,390 --> 00:02:04,800
[Jun Jiu Ling]

18
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:08,790
[Episode 25]

19
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:15,160
Chengyu, why do you think Young Master Ning

20
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:17,640
helped Jiuling?

21
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:21,000
Didn't I just say?

22
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:25,610
That was Jiuling's idea. But what is Young Master Ning's?

23
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:29,460
You probably already guessed.

24
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:33,410
You said that Jiuling and Young Master Ning discussed it.

25
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:37,770
But in the letter, neither Shopkeeper Liu nor Jiuling brought this matter up.

26
00:02:37,770 --> 00:02:41,520
That means this matter occurred suddenly.

27
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:45,450
How could something that happened suddenly be thought thoroughly about?

28
00:02:45,450 --> 00:02:48,110
Since he made the decision impulsively,

29
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:51,700
he has some feelings for her.

30
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:55,720
That would be the most reasonable explanation.

31
00:03:00,090 --> 00:03:02,120
Perhaps.

32
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:07,810
Chengyu, Jiuling getting help from Young Master Ning,

33
00:03:07,810 --> 00:03:09,950
are you happy about that?

34
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,440
I like her.

35
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:20,190
Her being liked and protected would make me happy for sure.

36
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:22,920
Regardless if that person is you or not?

37
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,540
Regardless if that person is me.

38
00:03:33,010 --> 00:03:37,180
As long as she is the one getting protected, it's fine.

39
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:43,450
Our Chengyu is really different from before.

40
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:52,570
Today is not a holiday, is someone getting married?

41
00:03:52,570 --> 00:03:57,020
Thinking of the date, it must be the congratulatory celebration for the first-ranked scholar.

42
00:03:57,570 --> 00:04:00,050
It's worthy of celebration.

43
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:03,340
Madam Ning must be very happy.

44
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:08,120
Yes, it is worthy of celebration.

45
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:15,880
This is nothing to be ecstatic about.

46
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:18,750
The magistrate is being too excessive.

47
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:20,630
He is the first-ranked scholar.

48
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,700
There is only one every three years.

49
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:25,800
It's normal to get excited.

50
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:30,490
Speaking of which, Yunzhao is of age to consider marriage.

51
00:04:30,490 --> 00:04:34,470
This child insists on discussing marriage after the examinations.

52
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,790
He has kept delaying it until now.

53
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:40,400
I wonder if Madam Ning has a favored candidate in mind.

54
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,350
There's no rush. There's no rush.

55
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:45,810
- Madam Ma.
- Congratulations, congratulations.

56
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:47,500
Two joyous events at once.

57
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:49,710
Please sit.

58
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:55,230
Madam Ma, our Ning family only produced one first-ranked scholar this year.

59
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:57,550
What two joyous events are there?

60
00:04:57,550 --> 00:05:00,400
You have yet to receive a letter from your family in the capital, right?

61
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:03,730
I let it slip. My apologies to you, Madam.

62
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:05,700
Now that Young Master Ning is the first-ranked scholar

63
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:08,660
and Miss Jun has a renowned reputation for treating the pox,

64
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:12,840
the sooner they get married, the sooner it's settled.

65
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,610
What do you mean?

66
00:05:14,610 --> 00:05:17,490
Jun Zhenzhen is getting married to my brother?

67
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:19,840
Is that the matter you are speaking of?

68
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:22,520
That is a misunderstanding.

69
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:26,200
We did have a marriage agreement previously but it has been broken off.

70
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,990
You don't need to hide it any longer.

71
00:05:27,990 --> 00:05:29,860
The Fang family's matters have been resolved.

72
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,320
There's no need to pretend going forward.

73
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:34,740
On the day after the ranking was announced, Young Master Ning

74
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:38,280
publicly announced the marriage arrangement with Miss Jun.

75
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:42,410
- They said they would get married after returning to their hometown.
- How is that possible?

76
00:05:42,410 --> 00:05:45,470
Why would my brother marry her?

77
00:05:57,170 --> 00:06:01,850
[Guanghua Gate]

78
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,680
Congratulations! Congratulations!

79
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,990
Say hello to Miss Jun for us!

80
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,740
Once getting married, will you let Miss Jun still practice medicine?

81
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:20,770
Please say hello to Miss Jun for us.

82
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:26,440
Miss, you clearly know that everyone will get into a frenzy seeing you, yet why did you still come?

83
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,460
Young Master Ning dared to help me in public,

84
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:31,040
so I must also be supportive of him in public.

85
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:35,820
In addition, that Lu guy will only be more cautious if more people know about this matter.

86
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:13,040
Second Brother, how do you feel?

87
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,240
Is there something you want to say?

88
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:19,950
Outstanding!

89
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:22,350
That was a soul-stirring sound.

90
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:25,020
It was unhypocritical and genuine. You did not wish them well but neither did you admit defeat.

91
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:28,800
That is the sound of the true feelings of a real man.

92
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:32,560
Bah!

93
00:07:33,130 --> 00:07:36,110
They only have an agreement on paper but are not yet actually married.

94
00:07:36,110 --> 00:07:39,200
I think Miss Jun treats you quite well.

95
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:43,730
- Bah.
- Stop making that sound anymore.

96
00:07:43,730 --> 00:07:46,160
I also think Miss Jun treats you quite well.

97
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,270
Bah!

98
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:51,000
Eldest Brother, why are some people so abnormal?

99
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:53,330
You are still young.

100
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:55,120
You will never understand.

101
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,030
Is that so?

102
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:03,020
Come, let's speak of serious matters.

103
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:04,810
Is there any news?

104
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:08,540
There hasn't been any criminal secretly put into jail.

105
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:12,420
We searched the entire capital yet still can't find Wan Qing.

106
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:25,600
You were hit because of Physician Jun, right?

107
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,040
Zhu Zhan.

108
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,240
The heir apparent of the duke?

109
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:39,980
It must be because you want to take in Physician Jun.

110
00:08:41,070 --> 00:08:45,270
Most likely he has taken a liking to Physician Jun.

111
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,800
Even though Physician Jun's family background is a bit lowly,

112
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:51,270
that is all right. Duke Cheng is not someone who cares about such trivial things.

113
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:54,100
He won't mind.

114
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:57,550
In that case, Physician Jun

115
00:08:57,550 --> 00:09:00,980
- can be Madam to the Heir Apparent.
- Impossible!

116
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:04,680
Ning Yunzhao also said that Jun Jiuling is his fiancée.

117
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,850
Ning Yunzhao?

118
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,650
The new first-ranked scholar?

119
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:17,540
If Physician Jun can marry him,

120
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:20,850
- then that is also very good.
- Impossible!

121
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:25,320
She is such a great young lady,

122
00:09:25,850 --> 00:09:28,180
You should let her live freely.

123
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:30,370
Isn't that a good thing?

124
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:35,520
Don't you like her very much?

125
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:39,410
Then I'll have her keep you company every day. Isn't that great?

126
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,720
No.

127
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:47,730
I also don't like her. She is not my younger sister.

128
00:09:50,350 --> 00:09:54,820
My younger sister... is already dead.

129
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,590
Since she seems so much like a princess,

130
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:05,010
then she should live like a princess.

131
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,860
If she refuses,

132
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:12,650
since Princess Jiuling is already dead,

133
00:10:13,140 --> 00:10:17,350
then what right does she have to be alive?

134
00:10:31,230 --> 00:10:36,190
[Elegance and Modesty]

135
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:43,480
Physician Jun, how is my wife?

136
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:47,040
Lord Wang, rest assured. Your wife's condition is not serious.

137
00:10:48,330 --> 00:10:52,280
I already gave her acupuncture and wrote her a prescription. She should recover soon.

138
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:56,000
Lord Wang, you should also comfort her and not let her be too agitated.

139
00:10:56,000 --> 00:11:00,140
That's great. You saying that my wife is fine is the biggest consolation for her.

140
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:03,760
No matter how much we say, your word means more to her.

141
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:06,740
- Lord Wang, you overpraise me.
- This way, please.

142
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:09,750
My Lord! It's bad, My Lord!

143
00:11:13,610 --> 00:11:15,620
What are you doing?

144
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:18,400
Wang Lian, someone reported you for corruption.

145
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:21,090
We are under orders to come search here.

146
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:25,850
You!

147
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:29,740
You are spouting nonsense! Search? Do you have an order to search?

148
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,900
This is enough!
[Martial Moral Ministry]

149
00:11:34,650 --> 00:11:37,890
So devious. Devious!

150
00:11:37,890 --> 00:11:41,630
My Lord! Madam has fainted!

151
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,400
Stay there!

152
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:47,370
Officials are working on a case. Those not involved should get lost!

153
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:49,050
I am a physician, so I have to go save someone.

154
00:11:49,050 --> 00:11:50,740
Who knows if you are going to save someone

155
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:53,840
or colluding with them to help them escape?

156
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,990
Lord Wang is such a beloved official.

157
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:02,520
The people from the Martial Moral Ministry just barged in accusing him of collusion. Based on what?

158
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:06,490
These people who search houses and destroy property don't care about the officials at all.

159
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:11,430
First, it was Secretariat Han, now it is Lord Wang.

160
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:16,580
Also, it always happens when I'm treating a patient there.

161
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:19,110
What does this have to do with us?

162
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:23,410
They must be targeting me.

163
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:26,150
This isn't Lord Lu's doing, is it?

164
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:29,040
Liu'er, relay the order to have the prescription gathered immediately.

165
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,320
You must select the best medicinal herbs

166
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:34,160
and send them to Lord Wang. There must be no delays.

167
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:36,600
- I must go see him.
- All right.

168
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:38,540
Rest assured, Miss.

169
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:42,390
However, you rejected his marriage proposal before. Would it be fine for you to go see him?

170
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:45,200
- I have no time to care about that. Go quickly.
- All right.

171
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:50,780
[Martial Moral Ministry]

172
00:13:03,370 --> 00:13:05,300
Lord Lu.

173
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:10,550
Looks like you finally understand my intentions.

174
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:13,940
- I don't understand.
- What don't you understand?

175
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,720
I want to give you a hard time.

176
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:18,420
I don't understand what you really want.

177
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:20,620
I'm someone with a marriage agreement.

178
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:23,410
So what? I like you.

179
00:13:23,410 --> 00:13:26,290
Is it wrong to sincerely propose a marriage?

180
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:35,440
Lord Lu, are you hoping that I will be like Third Madam?

181
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:37,200
No.

182
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,930
You two are not the same.

183
00:13:39,930 --> 00:13:43,240
You clearly know that you and I can never be together.

184
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:46,660
Lord Lu, remember this. I am a physician.

185
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:48,950
My responsibility is to treat illnesses and save people.

186
00:13:48,950 --> 00:13:52,860
If you want to give me a hard time next time, please don't harass the innocent.

187
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:13,620
[Li Residence]

188
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:16,090
Lord Huang, careful.

189
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:19,040
Be careful of the threshold.

190
00:14:21,730 --> 00:14:23,130
That's right.
[Li Residence]

191
00:14:23,130 --> 00:14:24,770
All right.

192
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:27,130
I will remember your words.

193
00:14:27,130 --> 00:14:29,220
Then, I shall trouble you, Lord Huang.

194
00:14:29,220 --> 00:14:33,070
Lord Huang, you work day and night for the nation. You need to take care of your health.

195
00:14:33,070 --> 00:14:36,010
I personally brewed some nourishing soup for you.

196
00:14:36,010 --> 00:14:39,010
Please try it, Lord.

197
00:14:39,010 --> 00:14:41,200
Noruishing soup?

198
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:43,910
Lord Li, I didn't expect you to know how to make nourishing soup.

199
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:46,620
I am embarrassed. When I was young, my family was not well off.

200
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,250
My mother was also ill often.

201
00:14:48,250 --> 00:14:50,660
So I personally washed clothes and cooked

202
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:52,960
in order to barely preserve warmth.

203
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:56,480
Then you truly worked hard, Lord Li.

204
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:59,830
Lord Huang, you're the one who is working hard!

205
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:02,940
I'm of low rank so I can't share your burdens.

206
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:06,980
- To be able to be of service to you, would be—
- Enough.

207
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:08,610
I understand.

208
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:13,560
Please accept this nourishing soup.

209
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:15,460
Please accept it.

210
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:27,270
This nourishing soup is indeed nutritious.

211
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:33,720
All right then. I'll see what positions are opened in court to assign you to.

212
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:37,760
After all, copying books in the Ministry of Personnel

213
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:40,640
- must be hard work.
- That's right.

214
00:15:42,050 --> 00:15:44,760
Here. Lord Huang.

215
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:49,150
May I ask, is that Prime Minister Huang?

216
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:53,320
Did you just come to the capital? That is not Prime Minister Huang. That is his son,

217
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,390
Young Lord Huang.

218
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:05,720
Step aside! Scram!
[Silence; Move Aside]

219
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,340
Step aside.
[Silence; Move Aside]

220
00:16:19,590 --> 00:16:22,110
Move! You!
[Silence]

221
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:23,640
Move! Go, go!

222
00:16:36,690 --> 00:16:40,310
Miss, who is that? So imposing.

223
00:16:40,310 --> 00:16:42,870
Prime Minister Huang's son, Huang Ziqing

224
00:16:44,830 --> 00:16:46,250
It looks quite lively up in front.

225
00:16:46,250 --> 00:16:48,580
- Let's go and take a look.
- Liu'er.

226
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:50,620
Next time you see him, stay far away. Do you understand?

227
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:52,250
Why?

228
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:54,920
Is he more scary than that Lu Yunqi?

229
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:57,570
It's said that many people died in the hands of the Martial Moral Ministry's officials.

230
00:16:57,570 --> 00:17:01,160
- However, he caused most of the deaths.
- What?

231
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:03,280
He's that scary?

232
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:05,800
Good thing we don't have much to do with him and can't offend him.

233
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,720
Let's take a detour.

234
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:14,800
- I'm sorry.
- My apologies.

235
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,760
Miss, your flowers.

236
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:20,040
Your flowers!

237
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:23,000
Isn't that Wan Qing, Wan Dachun's granddaughter?

238
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:25,680
Why does she seem so strange?

239
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,740
- Let's go and take a look.
- What?

240
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:31,480
- There are so many people today... 
- Lord Huang!

241
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:34,670
Young Lord Huang.

242
00:17:34,670 --> 00:17:37,970
Lord Tang, you're in such a rush. Is something the matter?
[Silence; Move Aside]

243
00:17:37,970 --> 00:17:40,830
The memorandum suggesting the impeachment of Duke Cheng by the Admonishment Court

244
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:44,080
has been blocked by Lord He once again.

245
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:50,180
When one gets old, his brain tends to get muddled.

246
00:17:50,180 --> 00:17:54,550
He actually said that our speculation of Duke Cheng's collusion with Northern Qi is foolish.

247
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:59,170
He even said the Imperial Censorate is supposed to write and present memorandums, not echoing hearsay like a dog barking.

248
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:01,740
How can Lord He scold people like that?

249
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:04,800
Exactly! The news from the North

