- Master.
 - Ziqing!
- Young Master, he...

287
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,990
Ziqing!

288
00:21:08,020 --> 00:21:09,990
Who are you?

289
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:14,600
Wan Qing.

290
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:19,210
I am the granddaughter of Wan Dachun from the Ministry of Works.

291
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:23,690
