292
00:21:23,690 --> 00:21:26,270
I will kill you!

293
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,340
So pitiful.

294
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:36,070
You unfilial son!

295
00:21:36,970 --> 00:21:41,200
