406
00:30:17,950 --> 00:30:19,810
Yes, My Lord.

407
00:30:23,450 --> 00:30:25,340
My son...

408
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:55,270
Slow down. Why are you in a rush?
[Jiuling Hall]

409
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:58,000
Why would Wan Qing choose a place like that to get revenge?

410
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,640
Isn't it clear that she no longer wants to live?

411
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:02,820
Don't speak rashly. We don't know what happened.

412
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:04,840
Thus, there's no justice in this world.

413
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:07,740
Justice comes at the expense of lives.

414
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:10,290
Miss, isn't it true?

415
00:31:11,770 --> 00:31:15,530
Jiuling, do you think the startled horse was truly just a coincidence?

416
00:31:24,100 --> 00:31:28,020
Baotang. Sanbing. Do me a favor and follow Wan Qing.

417
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:30,570
After the Huang servants leave her, take her out of the city.

418
00:31:30,570 --> 00:31:31,860
She's alive?

419
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:34,180
Yes, I gave her medicine to hold her breath for the time being.

420
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:37,050
She'll wake up tomorrow morning. Wan Qing,

421
00:31:37,610 --> 00:31:41,450
now that Huang Ziqing is dead, they definitely won't let you off.

422
00:32:08,690 --> 00:32:12,960
Did he startle the horse on purpose?

423
00:32:14,710 --> 00:32:17,180
You should ask him yourself.

424
00:32:18,950 --> 00:32:21,700
Why did it happen to be the young lord?

425
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,400
How did it go, Sanbing?

426
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:31,230
Don't worry. Baotang has taken Wan Qing out of the city.

427
00:32:31,230 --> 00:32:33,250
What about the young lord?

428
00:32:35,530 --> 00:32:37,840
No news yet.

429
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:46,780
He must've been worried I'd save Huang Ziqing, so he risked his life to do that.

430
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:50,210
When he insists on something, I can't stop him.

431
00:32:50,210 --> 00:32:53,910
Huang Ziqing happened to be submitting the memorandums about Duke Cheng's impeachment to His Majesty.

432
00:32:53,910 --> 00:32:58,140
Even if the young lord is silver-tongued, I'm afraid it'll be difficult for him to get out of this.

433
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:00,900
His life won't be in danger, will it?

434
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:03,010
Your Majesty!

435
00:33:04,510 --> 00:33:07,470
Zhu Zan killed my son.

436
00:33:09,450 --> 00:33:12,290
My family lineage was cut off because of the Zhu family.

437
00:33:12,290 --> 00:33:16,450
Considering the hard work I've done for the Imperial Court,

438
00:33:16,450 --> 00:33:20,860
